%e A397428 floor(7*phi) = 11, and floor(49*phi) = 79 are prime, so 7 is in the sequence.
%t A397428 r = (1 + Sqrt[5])/2;
%t A397428 Select[Range[120000], PrimeQ[#] && PrimeQ[Floor[#*r]] && PrimeQ[Floor[#^2 r]] &]
